            <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-8 text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
              Monitor every node, service, and task replica from a single agent on one manager node. Catch under-replicated services, crash-looping tasks, and lost manager quorum before they take down your stacks.
            </p>

            <div class="mt-10 flex items-center justify-center gap-x-6">
              <a href="/accounts/register"
